               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18371023-name-136" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-136" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-136" type="surname" value="FARMER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18371023-name-136" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN FARMER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am patrol of Farringdon Within. On the night of the 7th of October I saw the prisoner in St. Paul's-churchyard—I watched him, and saw him go into Mr. Rivington's shop and bring out two books in his hand, and directly he got outside he put them under his coat—I took him into custody, and took him into Mr. Rivington's—he had no books when he went in.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
